Cheers 2023 🥃

Eventually I will be back in the gym! Life throws us some interesting challenges in the forms of people, relationships, finance & health which sometimes needs attention & healing before putting anymore stress on the body 🙏🏽

How many of us do this with friends before we head out? Just incase on is in a dress, one in jeans, one in sweats 🤷🏻‍♀️ leggings for the win in almost every scenario for me 🙌🏽
#fitcheck #grwm #leggings #nike

This week coming at you like… 
2023 has already come at me with so many surprises and unexpected moments. I’ve given up trying to predict what’s to come 🤷🏻‍♀️ just be kind and try make the best of whatever life throws at you.. just don’t throw that pot at me 😳😂

Can’t wait to see what @xslasvegas & @patron have put together for Sunday while @realblackcoffee performs 🙌🏽 thank you always to @702skim & to @jonfong @shaun_mychal @jasminmedar @davidhadden #stagelife #patronelalto

Thank you to my beautiful friends for helping me celebrate my birthday 🥳 special thanks to @bellaloveslending for not letting me, not celebrate my birthday 😋 and @702skim & @wildboycox who always plan the best nights 🙌🏽
#hakkasan #lasvegas #birthday #bdayswithwildboy

Thank you to all who wished me a happy birthday! 🎉 
Lots of love to my Vegas fam who helped me celebrate ♥️ If I tagged you all I swear I’d get done for spamming 😂

The videos and clips over the past day have me rolling 🤣 the real time reactions to ‘DoEs ThIs AcCesS mY WiFi?’ Like yes.. apps, internet browsers and other phone features use the internet you have previously installed already in your home 🤨 Watch on the ‘other’ platform 😅 although I’m pretty sure it’s everywhere now as I’m seeing it on YT and twitch too 👾

🎰 🤠 🇺🇸

Oh hey there! ✨
August almost over already 🫣 moving into new apartment meant plenty of space for makeshift studio 🤗
Lots of little moments & big feels. August was a bit of a roller coaster 🎢  for those in these moments, thank you for being part of my story so far 🤗

What a day! ⛳️ Congratulations to the @vgkfoundation & @wynnlasvegas for hosting the 2023 Vegas Golden Knights Charity Golf Classic.  It was a long eventful day with the @vegasautogallery team finishing top 5 🙌🏽 
Received many questions about the car. If you are interested hit up @ken_tangen & @nick.dossa for this car & all other top sports & luxury cars.
